data.description: Take a look at this stunning single story home in the Pahrump, 89061 area! Beautiful desert landscaping in the frontyard for a clean look, and easy maintenance. As you walk in, you are greeted with a beautiful, long entryway. Open floor plan, neautral walls, and custom light fixtures. This home has been well kept, and taken care of by proud owners. 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a huge walk in closet in the primary bedroom. The 3 car garage comes with finished walls and epoxy flooring. As you walk out to the backyard, there is an abundance of space for hanging out, or entertaining. Real grass surrounds the backyard, along with a corner designated with pavers to truly make it your own space. Come schedule a showing today to see what else this beautiful home has to offer!
